SECTION 8: SECURITY REQUIREMENTS

1. Any derivative work must maintain equivalent security standards to
   those documented in the project's SECURITY.md file.

2. Security patches for vulnerabilities rated "Critical" or "High"
   must be applied within 30 days of release.

3. All deployments must include a mechanism for secure firmware updates
   with cryptographic verification.

4. Any modifications to security-critical components (authentication,
   cryptography, secure boot) must be audited by an independent third party.

Violation of these terms terminates your rights under this license.
